,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"智能叛變<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59afb66f85ad175eb816432da2f7e8c9f2b54d7a","tid":2048940,"uid":244493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:53:44.000Z","msg":"如果大媽40-50，計算一下，1970-1980出世，1976玩完文革，1978先玩改革開放，1998年工廠人工得200幾人仔，好彩有包食住。咁D女坐枱都一百至二百，咁女又冇讀書，冇技能，怕窮唔怕醜，咪出嚟做囉，咁做左幾年，自己就翻鄉下帶女去下海，自己做媽咪，做多幾年退休。咁D大媽存款清倉，見屯門咁得意，俾阿伯掂下就有錢收，又唔使瞓。以佢哋情況，有絕對利誘做啦，佢哋又唔怕冇面，因為乜嘢後生都出賣過，面皮好撚厚。<br />\n<br />\n大陸依家人口老化，正正就係呢一段年齡。缺乏信仰，道德，文盲。想生存，難得阿伯俾面，只要唔攪到其他人，就由他們吧。<br />\n<br />\n仲有一班60幾老嘢，娶過20-30幾大陸妹，絕對係害下一代，呢啲年輕力壯時娶唔到老婆，攪到五六十先娶，最仆街呢班loser, 社會問題就咁產生。"},{"pid":"810ce96188ec99980ce797002be8d047320c1fdf","tid":2048940,"uid":102984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"623eaacec1e8aa276501be8c0282b080030c65b5","tid":2048940,"uid":152209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f497d2a4cfa9e32ea939866564ab6d5ae41485b","tid":2048940,"uid":170375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3797479b5ddceb17cedddedecb9c3ad774064ed6","tid":2048940,"uid":10014,"like":66,"dislike":2,"score":64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:38:22.000Z","msg":"估唔到男人原來去到7、80就會吼返啲50歲阿嬋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔敢想像自己老左都會唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"冇錢 身材差<br />\n得50歲願比你摸下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:00:12.000Z","msg":"真 有錢個班未一樣摸返18歲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"唔夠有錢嘅會去買相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101c1c0005197b8d4673b90